header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Mercado Region - 2nd Round

videos.headline: Iowa State drains two 3-pointers to end the first quarter
videos.description: Iowa State gets 3-pointers from Kylie Feuerbach and Aubrey Joens to take a double-digit lead heading into the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Iowa State drains two 3-pointers to end the first quarter) 2021/3/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ashley Joens drains back-to-back 3s in third
videos.description: Ashley Joens has the hot hand for Iowa State, sinking two straight 3-pointers in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Ashley Joens drains back-to-back 3s in third) 2021/3/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa State bench loves its team's 15th 3-pointer of the game
videos.description: Kylie Feuerbach sinks a 3-pointer from the corner to put Iowa State up 66-57 vs. Texas A&M.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Iowa State bench loves its team's 15th 3-pointer of the game) 2021/3/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ashley Joens with the clutch and-1
videos.description: Ashley Joens gets the contested layup to fall while getting fouled and converts on the 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Ashley Joens with the clutch and-1) 2021/3/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Nixon ties it up for Texas A&M
videos.description: Jordan Nixon's tough bucket ties the game up at 75-75 with less than 10 seconds to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jordan Nixon ties it up for Texas A&M) 2021/3/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas A&M wins at the OT buzzer on Nixon's clutch shot
videos.description: Knotted at 82-82, Jordan Nixon drains the bucket as time winds down in overtime and the Aggies prevail.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Texas A&M wins at the OT buzzer on Nixon's clutch shot) 2021/3/24 ESHEET
